# Embedding VIB3+ in a Webpage

## Full-Page Background
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    .vib3-bg {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      z-index: -1;
    }
    .vib3-bg iframe {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      border: none;
    }
    .content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="vib3-bg">
    <iframe src="https://domusgpt.github.io/vib3-plus-engine/"></iframe>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <h1>Your Content</h1>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
```

## With Custom Settings
1. Go to https://domusgpt.github.io/vib3-plus-engine/
2. Configure the visualization (system, geometry, colors)
3. Press Ctrl+L to copy shareable URL
4. Use that URL in your iframe

## Controlling from Parent Page
```javascript
const iframe = document.querySelector('iframe');
iframe.contentWindow.switchSystem('holographic');
iframe.contentWindow.selectGeometry(11);
iframe.contentWindow.updateParameter('hue', 280);
```

# Common VIB3+ Recipes

## Purple Holographic Background
```javascript
window.switchSystem('holographic');
window.selectGeometry(11);  // Hypersphere Torus
window.updateParameter('hue', 280);
window.updateParameter('intensity', 0.6);
```

## Music Visualizer
```javascript
window.switchSystem('holographic');
window.toggleAudio();  // Enable audio
window.toggleAudioReactivity('bass', 'intensity', true);
window.toggleAudioReactivity('mid', 'rotation', true);
```

## Mouse-Reactive Background
```javascript
window.switchSystem('quantum');
window.selectGeometry(3);  // Torus
window.toggleSystemReactivity('quantum', 'mouse', true);
```

## Slow Ambient Animation
```javascript
window.switchSystem('faceted');
window.selectGeometry(5);  // Fractal
window.updateParameter('speed', 0.3);
window.updateParameter('chaos', 0.1);
```

## Geometry Cycling
```javascript
let geo = 0;
setInterval(() => {
  window.selectGeometry(geo);
  geo = (geo + 1) % 24;
}, 3000);
```
